9. Signature Line
This set forms the complete lineage architecture:  
a clean starting point,  
a responsible authority,  
a respectful transmission,  
a forward promise,  
a grounded oath,  
a unified charter,  
and a seal of integrity.

The line stands.  
The line is clean.  
The line moves forward with intention.

